OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772129063
OL,3,CFuture of UK's oldest roller coaster
OL,4,Cto be debated
OL,6,FThe future of Margate's most famous
OL,7,Flandmark is set to take centre stage
OL,8,Fat a meeting of Thanet District
OL,9,FCouncil today (Thursday 26 February).
OL,11,FCouncillors will gather to discuss a
OL,12,Fformal motion calling for "openness
OL,13,Fand transparency" from the owners of
OL,14,FDreamland following the shock
OL,15,Fannouncement that the Grade II listed
OL,16,FScenic Railway is to be "retired."
OL,18,FThe wooden rollercoaster, which dates
OL,19,Fback to 1920, is the oldest of its
OL,20,Fkind in the UK and serves as a global
OL,21,Fsymbol of seaside heritage.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772129063
OL,3,CFuture of UK's oldest roller coaster
OL,4,Cto be debated
OL,6,FHowever, owners Sands Heritage and
OL,7,FLive Nation recently confirmed the
OL,8,Fride would cease regular operation,
OL,9,Fciting safety and technical challenges.
OL,11,FThe motion, tabled by Labour Council
OL,12,FLeader Rick Everitt, expresses
OL,13,F"consternation" over the decision.
OL,14,FWhile acknowledging that the health
OL,15,Fand safety of visitors must be the
OL,16,Fpriority, Cllr Everitt argues that the
OL,17,Fpublic deserves to see the evidence
OL,18,Fbehind the closure.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772129063
OL,3,CFuture of UK's oldest roller coaster
OL,4,Cto be debated
OL,6,F"This has been a significant blow for
OL,7,FMargate and it is right that full
OL,8,Fcouncil has the opportunity to speak
OL,9,Fup on behalf of the community," Cllr
OL,10,FEveritt said.
OL,12,FHe revealed that while the council was
OL,13,Fgiven advance notice of the
OL,14,Fretirement, Dreamland has yet to hand
OL,15,Fover the technical reports used to
OL,16,Fjustify the move.
OL,18,FThe council is now taking a multi-
OL,19,Fpronged approach to investigate the
OL,20,Fdecision:
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
